      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, making it a fantastic choice for anyone who values quality and dependability. It drives smoothly and looks great, showing only the minor signs of careful use you'd expect from a well-maintained pre-owned car. Come see why this solid performer is the perfect addition to your driveway!",
